# Installation

Get started with Bioma 2.0 in your Angular project.

## Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+
- Angular 21+
- npm or yarn

## Install via npm

```bash
npm install @bioma/design-system
```

Or with yarn:

```bash
yarn add @bioma/design-system
```

## Setup

### 1. Import Styles

Add Bioma styles to your `angular.json`:

```json
{
  "styles": [
    "node_modules/@bioma/design-system/styles/tokens.css",
    "src/styles.scss"
  ]
}
```

### 2. Import Fonts

Add to your `index.html`:

```html
<head>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Rounded:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
```

### 3. Import Components

Components are standalone and can be imported individually:

```typescript
import { Component } from '@angular/core';
import { ButtonComponent } from '@bioma/design-system';

@Component({
  selector: 'app-root',
  standalone: true,
  imports: [ButtonComponent],
  template: `
    <bio-button label="Click me" variant="filled"></bio-button>
  `
})
export class AppComponent {}
```

## Using Design Tokens

Tokens are available as CSS custom properties:

```scss
.my-component {
  background-color: var(--primary-default);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  padding: var(--spacing-4);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
}
```

## Dark Mode

Enable dark mode by adding the `data-theme` attribute:

```html
<body data-theme="dark">
  <!-- Your app -->
</body>
```

Toggle programmatically:

```typescript
document.body.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');
// or
document.body.setAttribute('data-theme', 'light');
```

## TypeScript Support

Bioma includes full TypeScript definitions:

```typescript
import { ButtonSize, ButtonVariant } from '@bioma/design-system';

const size: ButtonSize = 'large';
const variant: ButtonVariant = 'filled';
```

## Troubleshooting

### Styles not loading
Verify the tokens.css file is imported in angular.json and the path is correct.

### Fonts not displaying
Check that the Google Fonts links are in your index.html and the network request is successful.

### Components not found
Ensure @bioma/design-system is installed and imported correctly in your component.

